                            <comment id="17942" author="sarah" created="Sat, 16 Jul 2011 02:18:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;with 32bitapi option, this test can pass&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/44178c04-af73-11e0-b33f-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/44178c04-af73-11e0-b33f-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17815" author="sarah" created="Thu, 14 Jul 2011 22:32:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry I didn&apos;t upload the result to Maloo, I ran it on build #201 rhel6/x86_64. &lt;br/&gt;
No, I didn&apos;t use 32bitapi option, here is the command I use to mount lustre on nfs server&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mount -t lustre -o flock 192.168.4.8@o2ib:/lustre /mnt/lustre&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will rerun and upload the result when the current tests finish&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17707" author="green" created="Thu, 14 Jul 2011 19:41:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;What run is this latest attachment from? There is no link in the archive or anywhere I can find.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Did you mount lustre on nfs server with -o 32bitapi? That&apos;s important bit that could lead to similar &quot;directory not empty&quot; problems.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16817" author="sarah" created="Wed, 22 Jun 2011 20:58:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;with the latest master build #180 metabench still failed on NFS3 &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5bde1fda-9d33-11e0-9a27-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5bde1fda-9d33-11e0-9a27-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15506" author="green" created="Fri, 3 Jun 2011 16:33:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The failure is different now:&lt;br/&gt;
Proc 0: Can&apos;t chmod to d0.metabench in /mnt/lustre/d0.metabench: Unknown error 521&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So it&apos;s a different issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(would likely be fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,892&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,892&lt;/a&gt; )&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15341" author="sarah" created="Tue, 31 May 2011 23:23:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;running metabench on the latest rehl6 build which contains &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-163&quot; title=&quot;compilebench fail on NFS v4 client&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-163&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-163&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix, got this error. &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/75a6bcba-8c17-11e0-aab9-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/75a6bcba-8c17-11e0-aab9-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15052" author="green" created="Wed, 25 May 2011 15:22:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Dupliate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-163&quot; title=&quot;compilebench fail on NFS v4 client&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-163&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-163&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Removed 72 files in      0.134 seconds&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;05/24/2011 23:47:44&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; FATAL error on process 3&lt;br/&gt;
Proc 3: Cant remove directory &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;/mnt/lustre/d0.metabench/TIME_CREATE_003.000&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: Directory not empty&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
